PhoneTap
========
PhoneTap enables you to record your own phone calls and then download them as a convenient .MP3 file. No hardware required, just input your number and the number you'd like to call. When you pick up we'll dial your requested number, record the call and we'll send you an email with a link to the download when you're done.


Install Instructions
====================

1. Create an AppEngine account: http://appengine.google.com/
2. Create a new AppEngine application
3. Download the AppEngine SDK: http://code.google.com/appengine/docs/python/gettingstarted/devenvironment.html
4. Update SENDER_EMAIL in PhoneTap/phonetap/settings.py to the email you used to sign up for AppEngine
5. Update the application variable in PhoneTap/app.yaml to whatever you named your application
6. Deploy the AppEngine application: http://code.google.com/appengine/docs/python/gettingstarted/uploading.html
7. Test the app